metadata.title: Eagle Nest Locations - PWS, Copper River
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This layer consists of eagle nest location point data for Prince William Sound and the Copper River Delta. The source agency (the US Fish and Wildlife Service (USF&WS)) has additional information such as nesting productivity and oil contamination.
